title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Hidden in the dining room breakfront, in a blue-enameled box bedecked with handpainted flowers, Molly Darrah keeps the keys to 18 neighbors' houses.” [From the San Francisco Chronicle, 10 February 1986.]
